channel.title: Tons of adds
channel.description:
I would like a script that would help me get points on www.tonsofadds.com
It's simple really. You just need it to go after you type in your friend ID and press the first picture in the top left, press back and do it again and again and so on.
If you could do this i'd be verrrrryy grateful. ;D
Thanks, TiggerZ
